# LIVE VAULT MATERIAL — never commit, never push.
# =================================================================
# This directory holds real credential material (GPG secret keys + the sealed SSH
# keylist), encrypted at rest under the store passphrase. Encrypted or not, it MUST
# NOT enter git — this brain repo has a remote. The material reaches the running brain
# by the seam SYNC (host -> distro drvfs copy), which is independent of git.
#
# Committed here: only the non-secret config (gh_auth.env), the docs (README.md), and
# this .gitignore. Everything else is runtime, created by `system/brain_sbin/gh_auth.py init`.
gpg_store/
*.gpg
ssh_keylist
*.key
*.pem
# transient host->brain secret/material drop (read in-distro via /opt/brain_truths, shredded after)
.transient/
!.gitignore
